properties.areaDesc: Penobscot Bay; Coastal Waters from Cape Elizabeth, ME to Merrimack River, MA out 25 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 11 at 3:20AM EST until January 12 at 4:00AM EST by NWS Gray ME
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and
seas 3 to 6 feet expected.

* WHERE...Penobscot Bay and Coastal Waters from Cape Elizabeth,
ME to Merrimack River, MA out 25 NM.

* WHEN...From 7 AM this morning to 4 AM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.
